special_powers.name: COSMIC ASSASSINATION
special_powers.description: Give Gamora a double power action. When you do, she can use Exploit Weakness as a free action, modifying her damage value by +1 for each 100 points of her target's point value.

special_powers.name: PURSUE THANOS TO THE ENDS OF THE UNIVERSE
special_powers.description: Give Drax the Destroyer a power action. Place him adjacent to an opposing character either named Thanos or with the Black Order keyword. Damage dealt to characters name Thanos by Drax the Destroyer is penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: FORCE FIELD DISMANTLER
special_powers.description: When moving, Drax the Destroyer ignores blocking terrain markers placed by the Barrier power, and removed them from the map if he moves into those squares. Adjacent opposing characters can't use Energy Shield/Deflection.

special_powers.name: THIS ONE NUDGED YOU TO JOIN
special_powers.description: Mantis can use Mind Control as if she had a range value of 7. When she does, she may target an adjacent friendly character with the Guardians of the Galaxy keyword even if that character has Battle Fury. Characters hit by Mantis through Mind Control modify their attack values by +1.

special_powers.name: PRECOG PRIEST OF PAMA
special_powers.description: Mantis can use Close Combat Expert and Probability Control.

special_powers.name: OCCUPY THE SAME PHYSICAL SPACE
special_powers.description: After an action resolves in which Starhawk took damage from an opposing character, you may replace him with GOTG #024 Aleta on the same click number.

special_powers.name: I'VE LIVED ALL THIS BEFORE
special_powers.description: Once per game, roll a d6 that can't be rerolled, minimum result 2. Place that many Past Lives tokens on this card. Give Starhawk a free action to remove a Past Lives token from his card and he can use Outwit and Probability Control until your next turn.

special_powers.name: CONTAINMENT SUIT BREACH
special_powers.description: Major Victory can use Toughness. When Major Victory is dealt penetrating damage, roll a d6. On 2-4 increase damage dealt to him by 1. On a result of 1, increase the damage dealt to him by 2.

special_powers.name: CARRYING ON CAP'S LEGACY
special_powers.description: Major Victory can use Leadership, Perplex and Telekinesis. When he uses Telekinesis, he may use it a second time as a free action, but only to place a friendly character with the Guardians of the Galaxy keyword.

special_powers.name: MINION: CENTRALIZED TARGETING
special_powers.description: When a friendly character with the Chitauri keyword and a higher point value is within 8 squares, Chitauri can use the Sharpshooter ability and modifies its range value by +2.

special_powers.name: HOVERCRAFT
special_powers.description: Chitauri Warleader has "Wing Transporter Symbol".

special_powers.name: COMAND PRESENCE
special_powers.description: Chitauri Warleader can use Leadership and Perplex. It may only target friendly character when using Perplex, and uses it twice if used Leadership to remove an action token from a character with the Chirauri keyword this turn.

special_powers.name: MINION: NEW ORDERS
special_powers.description: If a friendly character with the Kree keyword and higher point value is within 8 squares, Kree Private can use Sidestep. If there are at least two such characters, Kree Private can also use Incapacitate. If there are at least three such characters, Kree Private also modifies his combat values by +1.

special_powers.name: UNI-BEAM
special_powers.description: Captain Marvel can use Energy Explosion, Incapacitate, and Penetrating/Psychic Blast. When Captain Marvel hits with a ranged combat attack, hit targets can't make attacks during their next turn.

special_powers.name: DEFEND HUMANITY FROM MY PEOPLE
special_powers.description: Captain Marvel can use Defend and Super Senses. Modify the defense values of adjacent friendly characters without the Kree keyword by +1. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: SECRET GUARDIANS OF THE SHI'AR EMPIRE
special_powers.description: Raptor can use Sidestep and Stealth.

special_powers.name: BODY SWITCH IN NULL SPACE
special_powers.description: Give Darkhawk a free action. When you do, he modifies his defense value by -2 and can use Shape Change, but can't use any other powers or abilities until your next turn. At the beginning of your next turn, heal him to click #2.

special_powers.name: GRAPPLING HOOK
special_powers.description: When Darkhawk hits with a ranged combat attack and actions resolve, you may place the hit character in any square adjacent to Darkhawk.

special_powers.name: NEUTRALIZER LANCE
special_powers.description: Ikon can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast. When Ikon hits an opposing character, after actions resolve and until your next turn, that character can't use any powers or team abilities except for defense powers.

special_powers.name: KEEPING UP WITH THE COMPETITION
special_powers.description: Each time another friendly character with the Annhilators keyword or printed 4 damage hits one or more opposing characters and actions resolve, Ikon may make a close or ranged combat attack as a free action this turn if she hasn't hit a character with an attack this turn.

special_powers.name: MYSTICAL SHAPESHIFTERS
special_powers.description: Dire Wraith can use Shape Change. Once per turn, if the result is 1, you may reroll it.

special_powers.name: MEMORY LEECH
special_powers.description: Dire Wraith can use Precision Strike. When Dire Wraith KO's an opposing character, place that character on this card on any click. Dire Wraith can use any standard powers that character possesses on that click.

special_powers.name: MINION: AT THE COMMAND OF OUR QUEEN
special_powers.description: If a friendly character named Dire Wraith Queen is within 8 squares, Dire Wraith can use Sidestep.

special_powers.name: MYSTICAL SHAPESHIFTER QUDIRE WRAITH QUEENEEN
special_powers.description: Dire Wraith Queen can use Shape Change. Once per turn, if result is 1-2, you may reroll it.

special_powers.name: SHARED MEMORY LEECH
special_powers.description: Dire Wraith Queen can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast. When Dire Wraith Queen KO's an opposing character, place that character on this card on any click. Dire Wraith Queen and friendly characters named Dire Wraith can use any standard powers that character possesses on that click.

special_powers.name: VOLX'S MANIPULATIONS
special_powers.description: Dire Wraith Queen can use Perplex and Probability Control.

special_powers.name: DEFEND THE TWO EMPIRES - SHI'AR AND SPARTOI
special_powers.description: Spartoi Elite can use Defend. When he uses Defend, adjacent characters with the Shi'ar or Spartoi keyword also modify their defense values by +1 unless already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: DIVERT RESOURCES
special_powers.description: Spartoi Elite can use Perplex, but only to target other characters that are either occupy hindering terrain or share a keyword with him.

special_powers.name: GRAND ALLIANCE
special_powers.description: When you build your force, friendly characters with the Spartoi keyword also have the Shi'ar keyword.

special_powers.name: MY EARLY ADVENTURES WITH SHIP
special_powers.description: Jason of Sparta can use Charge and has "wing symbol". When he uses the Carry ability, he may carry up to 3 characters if they each share a keyword with him. Once per game, give Jason of Sparta a free action and he and characters he carried this turn can't be targeted by opposing characters until your next turn.

special_powers.name: RULER OF THE SPARTOI EMPIRE
special_powers.description: Jason of Sparta can use Leadership and Outwit. When he uses Leadership and succeeds, he may also remove an action token from any friendly character that shares a keyword with him within 3 squares.

special_powers.name: COLONIZE AND TERRAFORM ATMOSPHERE
special_powers.description: Once per game, if Rigellian Colonizer occupies an opponent's starting area and no opposing characters do, give Rigellian Conlonizer a double power action. If you do, for the rest of the game and at the begining of each of your turns, roll a separate d6 that can't be rerolled for each character without the Rigellian or Robot keyword and on a result of 6, deal that characater 1 penetrating damage. A character doesn't have this roll made more then once per turn, though the rolls must be made even if this ability is lost.

special_powers.name: DENSITY INCREASE
special_powers.description: Rigellian Colonizer can use Toughness. At the begining of your turn, if Rigellian Colonizer has no action tokens, you may modify Rigellian Colonizer's defense by +2 and she can use Invulnerability instead until your next turn. If you do, Rigellian Colonizer can't make an attack this turn.

special_powers.name: COLONIZE AND TERRAFORM LANDSCAPE
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Tana Nile a power action when she occupies an opponent's starting area but no opposing characters do. If you do, remove any number of debris tokens from the map, destroy any number of walls or squares of blocking terrain, and for the rest of the game, friendly characters can use Improved Movement: Elevated, Hindering and opposing characters can't ignore terrain for movement purposes even if this ability is lost.

special_powers.name: DENSITY INCREASE
special_powers.description: Tana Nile can use Toughness. At the beginning of your turn, if Tara Nile has no action tokens, you may modify Tana Nile's defense value by +2 and she can use Invulnerability instead until your next turn. If you do, Tana Nile can't make an attack this turn.

special_powers.name: IMAGE INDUCER
special_powers.description: Tana Nile can use Outwit and Shape Change.

special_powers.name: OBSERVER AND REPORT
special_powers.description: Recorder can use Outwit, but only to target adjacent characters. When a friendly character within line of fire is hit by an attack, after actions resolve, you may place Recorder adjacent to the attacker.

special_powers.name: ENGINEERED YOU FROM BIRTH
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, choose another friendly character with the Scientist keyword. Modify that character's speed and range values by +1 for the rest of the game, even if this ability is lost. If that character is also named Iron Man or Tony Stark, modify all of that character's combat values except damage by +1 instead.

special_powers.name: ARMOR OVERRIDE
special_powers.description: Recorder #451 can use Stealth and Mind Control. When he targets a character with the Armor, Robot, or Vehicle keyword with an attack, modify Recorder #451's attack value by +3.

special_powers.name: GODKILLER
special_powers.description: Give Recorder #451 a power action. Deal Recorder #451 1 unavoidable damage and for the rest of the game, the character chosen for his trait has "colossal damage symbol", "Power Cosmic team ability symbol", can use Impervious and modifies all of its combat values by +1.

special_powers.name: MINION: GENERATOR-ENHANCED
special_powers.description: Badoon and friendly characters with the Badoon keyword within 4 squares can use Stealth. If a friendly charater named "Brother Royal" is within 8 squares, Badoon can use Energy Explosion.

special_powers.name: TWIN LEADERS OF AN EMPIRE
special_powers.description: If there is exactly one other friendly Brother Royal on the map, modify Brother Royal's combat values by +1 and he can use Shape Change and Stealth.

special_powers.name: STRATEGY OF CONQUEST
special_powers.description: Give Brother Royal a free action and choose: Outwit or Perplex. Brother Royal can use the chosen power this turn even if he has already done so. Each time an opposing character is KO'd by a friendly character's attack, he can use this power again.

special_powers.name: INHUMANITY
special_powers.description: Triton can use Perplex. When he does, he can't modify damage values and may only target character with the Inhumans keyword within 3 squares.

special_powers.name: CYBERNETIC BODY
special_powers.description: Nebula can use Toughness, Willpower, and has "sharpshooter attack symbol".

special_powers.name: STEAL YOUR TRANSPORT
special_powers.description: Opposing characters can't use the Carry ability. If there is an opposing character possessing the Carry ability, Nebula modifies her speed value by +3 and can use the Carry ability.

special_powers.name: KREE STRATEGY - OVERWHELM
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters with the Kree keyword modify their attack value by +1 unless already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: KREE STRATEGY - DIVIDE
special_powers.description: Each opposing character that isn't adjacent to another opposing character modifies its defense value by -1 unless already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: LEADER OF THE KREE EFFORT
special_powers.description: Kree General can use Energy Explosion and Leadership. When he uses Leadership and succeeds, the action token he removes may be from any friendly character with the Kree keyword. If he does, then Kree General can't use Stealth this turn.

special_powers.name: STRATEGIC MANEAUVER
special_powers.description: Kree General can use Outwit. Give Kree General a power action and place him in any square within 6 squares to which no opposing character has a clear line of fire.

special_powers.name: MINION: SERVANT CLASS
special_powers.description: If a friendly character with the Inhumans keyword and a higher point value is within 4 squares, you may give Alpha Primitive a free action to move as if it had a speed value of 4.

special_powers.name: LIMITED INTELLIGENCE
special_powers.description: When Alpha Primitive is targeted by Outwit, counter all of its powers. When Alpha Primitive is targeted by Mind Control, modify its defense value by -2. Friendly characters not named Alpha Primitive can use Mind Control, but only to target Alpha Primitive. When they do, Alpha Primitive is dealt 1 unavoidable damage after actions resolve unless the attacking character is named Maximus.

special_powers.name: LIVING UP TO CAPTAIN MARVEL'S LEGACY
special_powers.description: Once per game when Captain Marvel would be KO'd, instead roll a d6 that can't be rerolled. On a result of 1-3, turn her to click #7 and modify her combat values by -1 this game. On a result of 4-5, turn her to click #6. On a roll of 6, turn her to click #5 and modify her combat values by +1 this game.

special_powers.name: TRAINED PILOT
special_powers.description: Captain Marvel can use Energy Shield/Deflection.

special_powers.name: SEVENTH SENSE
special_powers.description: Captain Marvel can use Outwit and Probability Control.

special_powers.name: IDEAL GENETIC MATE
special_powers.description: When Dr. Minerva is adjacent to a friendly character named Captain Atlas or Captain Marvel, modify all of their combat values by +1.

special_powers.name: EXPERIMENT ON YOU TO IMPROVE OUR SPECIES
special_powers.description: Once per game before an adjacent opposing character with one or two action tokens takes damage from Dr. Minerva's attack, you may choose a standard power that character can use. Until the end of the game, friendly characters with the Kree keyword can use that power.

special_powers.name: PSYCHE-MAGNETRON EXPOSURE
special_powers.description: Dr. Minerva can use Perplex. She can use it normally or, when she targets a character with the Kree keyword, she may modify any combat value except damage by +2.

special_powers.name: TEMPORARY ALLIANCE, SEALED BY MARRIAGE
special_powers.description: When you build your force, friendly characters with the Kree keyword also have the Inhumans keyword.

special_powers.name: INVISIBILITY CLOAK
special_powers.description: Ronan the Accuser can use Sidestep. Ronan the Accuser can't be targeted by non-adjacent opposing characters unless he made an attack during your last turn.

special_powers.name: PURSUER TEMPLATE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, choose an opposing character. If that character has one or more action tokens, give Korath the Pursuer a free action to move up to 3 squares.

special_powers.name: BETA BATONS
special_powers.description: Korath the Pursuer can use Energy Explosion and Ranged Combat Expert. When he uses Ranged Combat Expert, he may activate Energy Explosion.

special_powers.name: DETECTING NON-KREE BRAIN PATTERNS
special_powers.description: Korath the Pursuer can use Outwit. If no opposing character has the Kree keyword, he can use it a second time.

special_powers.name: YAKA ARROWS
special_powers.description: Give Yondu a power action. Make a ranged combat attack targeting a single opposing character regardless of line of fire.

special_powers.name: OCCUPY THE SAME PHYSICAL SPACE
special_powers.description: After an action resolves during which Aleta took damage from an opposing character, you may replace her with GOTG #004 Starhawk on the same click number.

special_powers.name: SOLID LIGHT SHIELD
special_powers.description: Aleta can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Toughness. Adjacent friendly characters can use Energy Shield/Deflection.

special_powers.name: WORDS, WORDS, WORDS
special_powers.description: Whenever an opposing character uses Outwit, Perplex or Probability Control, place a Whisper token on this card. Give Ebony Maw a free action and remove a Whisper token to use either Outwit, Perplex or Probability Control until your next turn if he can't already. He may be given this free action up to three times each turn.

special_powers.name: CULL OBSIDIAN
special_powers.description: When Ebony Maw is KO'd by an opposing character's attack, deal damage to that character equal to the last amount of damage dealt to Ebony Maw. This damage can't be reduced below 1.

special_powers.name: TWIST YOU INTO BETRAYAL
special_powers.description: Whenever Ebony Maw is targeted with an attack from an opposing character, you may choose an adjacent opposing character that isn't the attacker to be the target of that attack even if that character couldn't normally be targeted.

special_powers.name: INHUMANITY
special_powers.description: Crystal can use Perplex, but can't modify damage values and may only target a character with the Inhumans keyword within 3 squares.

special_powers.name: INHUMANITY
special_powers.description: Gorgon can use Perplex, but can't modify damage values and may only target a character with the Inhumans keyword within 3 squares.

special_powers.name: BULL RUSH
special_powers.description: Gorgon can use Charge. When he does and moves in a direct line, modify his attack value by +1 for every 2 squares he moved.

special_powers.name: QUAKE STOMP
special_powers.description: Gorgon can use Quake. When he does, opposing characters within 3 squares are considered adjacent.

special_powers.name: ALWAYS SEE THE WEAK SPOT
special_powers.description: Damage dealt by Karnak is penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: INHUMANITY
special_powers.description: Karnak can use Perplex, but can't modify damage values and may only target a character with the Inhumans keyword within 3 squares.

special_powers.name: PSYCHIC INTRUSION
special_powers.description: Moondragon can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast. When she does, after actions resolve she may use Mind Control to target a hit character as a free action.

special_powers.name: GUARD THE WHOLE GALAXY
special_powers.description: Friendly characters with the Guardians of the Galaxy keyword may replace their defense values with the highest printed defense values among friendly characters with that keyword.

special_powers.name: TACTICAL MANEUVER
special_powers.description: Star-Lord can use Outwit. When he does, he can count range and draw lines of fire from any friendly character that shares a keyword with him.

special_powers.name: BLACK NOVA HELMET
special_powers.description: Nova can use Running Shot and Stealth.

special_powers.name: I WONDER HOW MUCH POWER I CAN GENERATE
special_powers.description: Nova can use Pulse Wave. When he does and his damage value would be replaced with 1, you may choose to replace it with 2 instead. If you do, deal Nova 1 unavoidable damage after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: PERFECT SEDUCTION
special_powers.description: Starfox can use Mind Control with a range value of 10. When he does, before the attack, you may choose 1, 2 or 3, lower than his target's click number. Increase his and his target's attack value by the chosen amount. After actions resolve, heal the character hit by Starfox by the amount chosen.

special_powers.name: I PSIONICALLY STIMULATE YOUR BRAIN
special_powers.description: At the end of your turn, you may roll a d6 that can't be rerolled for each other friendly character within 3 squares. On a result of 6, heal that character 1 damage.

special_powers.name: HUNT THE HELLISH TO THE ENDS OF THE EARTH
special_powers.description: When an opposing character targets Angela, after actions resolve you may place a Prey token on that character's card. Give Angela a power action to be placed adjacent to an opposing character with a Prey token on its card. Then make a close combat attack as a free action targeting that character.

special_powers.name: YOU'LL MAKE A FINE ADDITION
special_powers.description: When Collector hits a lower point character with a close combat attack and his attack total is at least 3 higher than his target's defense value, you may place the hit character on this card. Collector considers that character as Collected as long as it is on this card.

special_powers.name: I WON'T LET YOU ESCAPE
special_powers.description: At the end of your turn, place an Exhibit token on each Collected character's card, and roll 2d6 that can't be rerolled. Each Collected character rolls 2d6 and subtracts the number of Exhibit tokens on its card from the result. If a Collected character's result is equal or higher than yours, that character's controller may place it within 6 squares of Collector with an action token and remove all Exhibit tokens from its card. Opposing characters can be given a power action to remove an Exhibit token from a friendly character. When the game ends, all Collected characters are KO'd.

special_powers.name: LET ME SHOW YOU THE TRUE FORM OF MY POWER
special_powers.description: Collector can use Shape Change. Each time Collector is hit, after actions resolve modify his combat values by +1 until the end of your next turn, even if this power is lost.

special_powers.name: ENCODED WITH ALL HUMAN KNOWLEDGE AND CULTURE
special_powers.description: Killraven can use Outwit and Improved Targeting: Characters. When he uses Outwit, he may instead target all opposing characters within 3 squares and line of fire and counter one power each.

special_powers.name: INHUMANITY
special_powers.description: Black Bolt can use Pulse Wave and Improved Targeting: Destroy Blocking. When he uses Pulse Wave, the attack generates knock back and each hit character is knocked back 3 squares.

special_powers.name: SONIC ANNIHILATION
special_powers.description: Black Bolt can use Pulse Wave and Improved Targeting: Ignores Blocking Terrain. When a ranged combat attack resolves, any blocking terrain along its line of fire to the target is destroyed. When he uses Pulse Wave, the attack generates knock back and each hit character is knocked back 3 squares.

special_powers.name: TRANSPORT THE ROYAL FAMILY
special_powers.description: Lockjaw can use the Carry ability. He may carry up to three characters that share a keyword with him regardless of their speed symbols.

special_powers.name: INHUMANITY
special_powers.description: Lockjaw can use Perplex, but cant' modify damage values and may only target a character with the Inhumans keyword within 3 squares.

special_powers.name: INHUMANITY
special_powers.description: Maximus can use Perplex, but can't modify damage values and may only target a character with the Inhumans keyword within 3 squares.

special_powers.name: ALPHA PRIMITIVE
special_powers.description: Twice per game, give Maximus a power action and place GOTG #018 Alpha Primitive on the map in an adjacent square.

special_powers.name: MENTAL OVERRIDE
special_powers.description: Maximus can use Mind Control. When he does, modify his attack value by 4 minus the number of squares to the target. If he hits, modify his target's attack value by the same amount.

special_powers.name: PUTTING THE "MAD" IN MAD SCIENTIST
special_powers.description: Maximus can use Outwit. When he does, roll a d6 that can't be rerolled. On a result of 1, he loses this power until your next turn. On a result of 5-6, he may immediately use Outwit again. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: INHUMANITY
special_powers.description: Medusa can use Perplex, but can't modify damage values and may only target a character with the Inhumans keyword within 3 squares.

special_powers.name: DEADLY LOCKS
special_powers.description: Medusa can use Charge and Plasticity. During the beginning of your turn, give Medusa a free action and deal 1 penetrating damage to a single adjacent opposing character with 1 or more actions tokens.

special_powers.name: SHADOW AGENT OF OBLIVION
special_powers.description: Martyr can use Hypersonic Speed and Stealth.

special_powers.name: MARTYR TO OBLIVION
special_powers.description: Give Martyr a free action and deal her 1 unavoidable damage and choose one: heal all adjacent friendly characters 1 click or heal one adjacent friendly character 2 clicks.

special_powers.name: EBONY WEAPONS OF OBLIVION
special_powers.description: Deathurge can use Blades/Claws/Fangs and deals penetrating damage while using it. When Deathurge rolls a d6 for Blades/Claws/Fangs, the maximum result is the click number of his target. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: ABSTRACT ENTITY
special_powers.description: Deathurge can use Shape Change and Super Senses.

special_powers.name: LIFE NOT SEEM WORTH IT?
special_powers.description: Deathurge can use Poison. If an adjacent opposing character is on a click number higher than its printed damage value, this damage is penetrating.

special_powers.name: THE DREAM OF A GODLESS AGE
special_powers.description: Gorr the God Butcher modifies his attack value by +2 when targeting a character with the Deity keyword with an attack. Gorr the God Butcher deals penetrating damage to characters with the Deity keyword.

special_powers.name: ALL-BLACK THE NECROSWORD
special_powers.description: Gorr the God Butcher can use Barrier, Blades/Claws/Fangs, and Smoke Cloud. When he rolls a 1-3 for Blades/Claws/Fangs, he can use Barrier and Smoke Cloud each as free actions after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: GODBOMB
special_powers.description: Give Gorr the God Butcher a double power action and he can use Pulse Wave as a free action. When he does, modify his range value by the number of opposing characters on the map and he deals damage equal to that number, maximum 4, no matter what his damage value is.

special_powers.name: CAUGHT IN A TIME LOOP
special_powers.description: Give Sphinx a free action and place a Time Loop special marker in his square if none placed by him are on the map. At the beginning of your turn, you may place him in the square with his Time Loop special marker, then remove it.

special_powers.name: ABSORB XANDAR
special_powers.description: Sphinx can use Outwit, Perplex, Power Cosmic Team Ability, and has the Colossal damage symbol.

special_powers.name: CHRONAL DUPLICATE
special_powers.description: Sphinx can use Probability Control and Shape Change.

special_powers.name: A TWISTED MOTHER
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters with the Maximum Carnage keyword modify their attack and defense values by +1. If Shriek took damage from an attack since your last turn, one friendly character with the Maximum Carnage keyword can use Charge as a free action, but while using it may only attack a character that damaged Shriek since your last turn

special_powers.name: A DOUBLE BLAST FROM HER PSYCHIC SHOTGUN
special_powers.description: When Shriek hits a single character with a ranged combat attack that deals damage, modify that character's combat values by -1 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: CARNAGE IS THE BATTERY, AND I'M THE RADIO!
special_powers.description: Characters within range that do not have the Maximum Carnage keyword possess Battle Fury. Shriek can use Mind Control, and when she does she can target any opposing characters within range regardless of line of fire or Battle Fury, and she isn't dealt unavoidable damage from Mind Control.

special_powers.name: TELEPORT ON TITAN
special_powers.description: I.S.A.A.C. can use Phasing/Teleport, the Carry ability, and Stealth. Give I.S.A.A.C. a power action and place him in any square closer to your starting area than any other starting area.

special_powers.name: EVERYTHING THAT HAPPENS ON TITAN IS KNOWN
special_powers.description: I.S.A.A.C. can use Outwit. When he does he can use Improved Targeting: Elevated, Hindering, Blocking.

special_powers.name: CULL OBSIDIAN
special_powers.description: When Black Dwarf is KO'd by an opposing character's attack, deal damage to that character equal to the last amount of damage dealt to Black Dwarf. This damage can't be reduced below 1.

special_powers.name: I SHALL NEVER FAIL YOU AGAIN
special_powers.description: Black Dwarf can use Charge and Flurry.

special_powers.name: SEISMIC SLAM
special_powers.description: Black Dwarf can use Quake and Super Strength. When he uses Quake, choose up to 2 hit characters to be dealt 3 damage instead of 2 and knocked back 3 squares.

special_powers.name: CHOOSE - THE GAUNTLET OR THE TRIBUTE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your first turn, each opponent chooses one: Deal 1 damage to each character on his or her force 100 points or less; or choose a character on his or her force 101 points or more and deal that character 3 damage. Opponents can't choose an option for which they have no characters.

special_powers.name: A BLOODY PATH TO FIND MY SON
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your first turn, choose an opposing character. Thanos' attacks deal 1 additional damage to that character. When that character is KO'd choose another opposing character.

special_powers.name: BEYOND YOUR MORTAL CONCERNS
special_powers.description: Thanos can't be assigned a relic or resource.

special_powers.name: THE BLACK ORDER OBEYS
special_powers.description: Thanos can use Leadership. When he does and succeeds, he may remove the action token from any character with the Black Order keyword anywhere on the map.

special_powers.name: [300 PTS] BUILT TO TEST MY FOES: AVENGERS
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within range can't use team abilities and lose their keywords. At the beginning of the game, you may choose that Thanosi can use one of his other traits this game instead of this one.

special_powers.name: [200 PTS] BUILT TO TEST MY FOES: THOR
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within range can't ignore pushing damage. At the beginning of the game, you may choose that Thanosi can use Build to Test My Foes: Ka-Zar this game instead.

special_powers.name: [100 PTS] BUILT TO TEST MY FOES: KA-ZAR
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within range can't ignore terrain for movement purposes.

special_powers.name: CULL THE OBSIDIAN
